id: pm-7n5a
title: "Sentry PM-CLI-29: external Neo4j command reports missing configuration as a high pm-cli error"
description: "Investigate and correctly classify or re-home the live Sentry high CommandError emitted when an external Neo4j command runs without NEO4J_URI, NEO4J_USER, and NEO4J_PASSWORD. The pm-cli repository contains no Neo4j implementation or configuration references, so ownership likely belongs to an extension or downstream integration; prevent unrelated external expected-configuration errors from blocking pm-cli release gates while preserving actionable attribution."
type: Issue
status: open
priority: 1
tags[3]: "area:observability",external-integration,sentry
